data.description: Buy this house! Assumable loan with 2.99 percent interest! Save over $100K on interest alone in comparison to todays rates. The Buyer does NOT have to be a veteran to apply, however, they must still qualify for the loan, be owner occupants as primary residence, and pay the difference between contract price and loan balance as down payment. Email listing agent for more details. Near HWY 80 and easy access to Heath and Rockwall as well. The house is all you need with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on a split floorplan. Nice size backyard with covered patio. Seller is leaving the fridge and washer and dryer. Very lightly lived in, this home is move in ready. Travis ranch community amenities. Property has solar panels that buyer must assume upon purchase. Ask listing agent for details.
